<%- include('../partials/header', { title: title }) %>

<article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto my-8 p-6 md:p-8 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200"><%= title %></h2>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-6">
        <section>
            <h3>For Buyers:</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Browse Products:</strong> Explore listings on the homepage or by category.</li>
                <li><strong>Find What You Need:</strong> Click on a product to see more details.</li>
                <li><strong>Contact Seller Directly:</strong> Use the seller's phone number (clearly displayed) to call or SMS them.</li>
                <li><strong>Arrange Purchase:</strong> Discuss price, quantity, pickup, or delivery directly with the seller.</li>
            </ol>
            <p class="p-3 bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 text-yellow-800 rounded-md">
                <strong>Important:</strong> This website only connects you. All transactions and arrangements are made directly between you and the seller. We do not handle payments or deliveries.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h3>For Producers (Farmers & Handmakers):</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Register:</strong> Create an account with your name/business name, phone number, and location.</li>
                <li><strong>Log In:</strong> Access your producer dashboard.</li>
                <li><strong>Add Products:</strong> List your items with details like name, description, price, and an optional photo. Your registered phone number is automatically shown.</li>
                <li><strong>Manage Listings:</strong> Edit or delete your products as needed.</li>
                <li><strong>Connect with Buyers:</strong> Buyers will see your phone number and contact you directly via call or SMS to purchase your goods.</li>
            </ol>
            <p>Our goal is to make it easy for you to reach local customers!</p>
        </section>
    </div>
</article>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>